## 📌 Task 2 – Tool Installation & Snapshots

Installed all required tools on **Ubuntu 20.04** running inside **Oracle VirtualBox**.  
System configuration:  
- **RAM:** 6 GB  
- **HDD:** 50 GB  
- **vCPU:** 4  

### 🔧 Installed Tools
1. **Yosys** – RTL synthesis tool  
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/YosysHQ/yosys.git
   cd yosys
   make config-gcc
   make
   sudo make install
2.Icarus Verilog (iverilog) – Verilog simulator

sudo apt-get install iverilog

3.GTKWave – Waveform viewer

sudo apt-get install gtkwave

4.ngspice – Analog/mixed-signal simulator

tar -zxvf ngspice-37.tar.gz
cd ngspice-37/release
../configure --with-x --with-readline=yes --disable-debug
make
sudo make install

5.Magic – Layout tool

git clone https://github.com/RTimothyEdwards/magic
cd magic
./configure
make
make install

6.OpenLANE – Digital design flow

git clone https://github.com/The-OpenROAD-Project/OpenLane
cd OpenLane
make
make test

